data.description: Welcome to this modern and beautifully updated 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom block home nestled in the heart of Seminole! Boasting 1075 square feet of living space on a spacious 7039 square foot lot, this home is a true gem.    Step inside to discover a host of recent updates, including wood vinyl plank flooring, hurricane-rated double pane vinyl windows, and hurricane shutters, creating a sleek and secure interior. The newer interior doors add a touch of contemporary elegance, while the updated bath and stunning kitchen with granite countertops, tile backsplash, and stainless steel appliances elevate the home's modern appeal.    The practicality of this home is evident with its indoor laundry room and 2nd bath, conveniently located off the 1-car garage, and providing additional access to the large fenced backyard, patio, and sunroom.    This property also features a roof installed in 2009 and a HVAC system from 2016, ensuring both comfort and peace of mind for the new owners. Security cameras convey to new owner.    Located just minutes from the Pinellas Trail, parks, tennis courts, and the Seminole City Center, this home offers easy access to a variety of recreational amenities. Not to mention, the proximity to gorgeous beaches makes it an ideal retreat for those who appreciate coastal living.    Don't miss the opportunity to make this modern and updated home your own. Schedule a showing today and experience the best of Seminole living!
